//data burung Stone Magpie Bird The first type of bird is the stone magpie. For lovers of chirping birds, the stone magpie is like a prima donna and top artist. Because its chirping is very melodious. In addition, it is able to imitate the sounds of other birds. Canaries Behind its small body, walnuts have a distinctive chirping. In fact, the sound of a canary has its own term, namely cringe Cucak Rowo This type of bird is no stranger to chirping bird fans. This is because he is known as a loud, clear and superior sound maker compared to other types of birds. The price is also quite expensive because the maintenance and captivity process is quite difficult. Cendet This bird has many names, namely cender, pletet, pentet, to parrot toet. Besides being equipped with a loud and melodious voice, the appearance of the cendet bird is so charming and elegant Colored Birds Like a bird that came down from heaven, the five colors are so attractive to the eye because of their beauty
//data kucing Domestic Cat This cat very often roams the streets and it is also very easy for you to recognize its characteristics. In contrast to purebred cats that have distinctive characteristics and require special care, domestic cats do not have their own special characteristics and care. Persian cat This cat has long thick hair, a round face, and a snub nose. Anggora Cat This cat is in great demand because of its very distinctive physical characteristics, namely dense snow-white fur and fairly wide ears. Siamese Cat The Siamese cat is an oriental cat that is very easy to find in Thailand. Ragdoll cat Ragdolls are a popular breed of cat because they love humans so much. Because of his love, the cat often follows his owner around the house from morning to night.
